Data Manipulation

The DataCamp modules also helped me learn how to do data manipulation in R to get the optimal configuration of available factors in a dataset:

library(dplyr)
library(hflights)
hflights <- hflights %>%
  mutate(
    CancellationCode = ifelse(CancellationCode == "", "E", CancellationCode)
  )

table(hflights$CancellationCode)
     A      B      C      D      E 
  1202   1652    118      1 224523
